channel.title: XileSoft REVISION 6.78 (ALL SKILLS! HOLDS 500+ PLAYERS! TONS OF STUFF!)
channel.description:
[center]
[b]XileSoft[/b] [i]Created by Canownueasy[/i]
[size=5][b][url=http://www.mediafire.com/?o4n5mwmaaun][DOWNLOAD][/url][/b][/size]
[COLOR=Blue][b]Stability[/b][/COLOR]
Stability. Definately the most important part of a server. NOBODY wants to play a server that laggs constantly or disconnects every 15 or so minutes. What I am
offering here is an 100% LAG FREE server as long as you have 250 or less players online, and can hold up to 782 players (TESTED) without disconnecting.
[COLOR=Blue][b]Player Verse Player[/b][/COLOR]
[b]Combat is to it's fullest.[/b]
Perfect melee. When I say perfect, [b]I MEAN IT[/b]. Considering XileSoft is based off of [b]Final Devolution 2.7[/b], and Killamess's combat was near 99%, I added the final touches to melee. <3
Near perfect range. Perfect projectiles, delays, drawbacks, maxhits, ect. Darts for those farcast killers, and magic shortbows for those gmaul comboers.
Very decent mage. I'll tell you the truth, mage isn't 100%, not even 90%, but however, [b]IT BEATS DELTASCAPE's[/b]. Projectiles are perfect, delays are near perfect.
No autocasting (I WILL MAKE IN NEXT REVISION)
[COLOR=Blue][b]Skills[/b] [/COLOR] [b]Woodcutting[/b]
Near perfect woodcutting. Delays for woodcutting, level requirements, almost everything. It's simply awsome.
[b]Firemaking[/b]
Near perfection! Was around 85% that Killamess realeased, I reamped it to walk west and light fires faster based upon levels now making it near perfect! <3
[b]Mining[/b]
To hand it to ya, mining isn't at it's best. Around 65%-75%. Includes animations, level up, level requirements, does [b]ALL ROCKS[/b].
[b]RuneCrafting[/b]
Simple RuneCrafting. RuneCrafting is a basic skill for the server, but it works. All altars work, delays, animations, level up, ect. Does [b]ALL ALTARS[/b].
[b]Fishing[/b]
Fishing will be added in the next revision realease! Sorry!
[b]Cooking[/b]
Cooking will be added in the next revision realease! Sorry!
[b]Fletching[/b]
Fletching is 99% perfect. Use the items on the other items. Includes level up, animations, delays. It's a bucket of soup.
[b]Theiving[/b]
Near 99% theiving. Stalls with disappearing items in them after you theive. Delays, animation support, level up, stall support, npc theiving support.
(GUARDS FOR STALLS WILL COME IN NEXT REVISION)
[b]Agility[/b]
Agility IS AMAZING. Around 95%-98%. Walking, animations, level up, delays, courses, ALL INCLUDED.
[COLOR=Blue][b]NPC Combat[/b][/COLOR]
When you look at a server, you want to see perfect pvp right? What about nvp? NPC Combat is about 95% perfect. NPC's can use mage. Bosses are an easy add. NOW SUPPORTS
MELEE/RANGE, MELEE/MAGE, RANGE/MAGE, and MELEE/RANGE/MAGE support to add your bosses! Includes bosses: King Black Dragon, Demon of Zykum
[COLOR=Blue][b]Minigames[/b][/COLOR]
Minigames are a HUGE part of servers. Ever hear people coming onto your server and saying "are there minigames and stuff here" - well with
XileSoft there are lots of them, so you can answer "YES!"
Minigames include:
[b]Barrows[/b]
Simple barrows. Kill the Barrows Brothers for a key which drops at a 1% chance. When you have key use it on chest for a random barrows prize.
[b]Blurite[/b]
A mining minigame! Mine Blurite ore until you have 1000 and bring to door. Open door and kill 50 Blurite Guards inside. You then teleport to the queen and the knights
of the blurite which are extremely hard! You need a Blurite Key to enter the Blurite Gate to receive your prize. Queen drops key at 50% rate, knights at 10% rate, and
if you are really lucky, guards at 1%! (QUEEN WILL SUPPORT RANGE/MAGE IN NEXT REVISION)
[b]Fight Pits[/b]
A fun PKing minigame! Fast paced PKing with timers, and multi combat support! (REWARDS WILL COME IN NEXT REVISION)
[b]Demon of Zykum[/b]
[b]FIGHT THE STRONGEST CREATURE IN THE GAME![/b] A fully perfected, fully custom NPC with [b]NO[/b] glitches what so ever! Kill the demon for Demon Horns which are
worth around 8K [b]EACH[/b] and they can drop anywhere from 0-10! Also, if you gather 1000 Demon Horns you can cash them in for a Demon set to become a demon! DEMON
SUPPORTS [b]FULL[/b] MELEE/RANGE/MAGIC AND MORE!
[b]Demon Challenge[/b]
Can you survive the raving demons? Demons everywhere attacking you with deadly strikes of blood! Kill them and get rewards and sometimes food! They also drop Demon
Horns at a 5% drop rate and you can get anywhere from 0-3! SUPPORTS [b]FULL[/b] MAGE.
[b]God Wars[/b]
WiLL BE HERE IN NEXT REVISION! REDOING THINGS! =)
[b]Jad[/b]
WILL BE HERE IN NEXT REVISION!
NEED TO REDO! :(
[b]PK Box[/b]
Needed to re do it! Will be here in next revision though!
[b]Assualt[/b]
Need to re do it! Will be here in enxt revisiON!!
[b]Zombie Survival[/b]
Going to be one of the best minigames, started it already =D will be here in the next revision, or the revision after that. WORKING HARD ON IT =)
[COLOR=Blue][b]Creativity![/b] [/COLOR] What can I say, I've made almost everything interactive just like RuneScape! Click random objects to see appealing messages!
[COLOR=Blue][b]Credits[/b][/COLOR]
Canownueasy - A ton of shit Killamess - Base Aaron (Iw RANGE wI or Lost-Souls on Locus) - Some shit JohnnyJ - Some ladder shit
[/center][br][br][size=1]Posted on: November 26, 2009, 07:15:38 pm[/size][hr][B]Images of Gameplay[/B]
